---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Julian Molina-Goni">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 text-center">About</h1>

      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16">
        I'm Julian Molina-Goni, a <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Full-Stack Cloud Engineer</span> with over
        10 years of experience across cloud infrastructure, DevOps, automation, and full-stack development. I help businesses
        automate workflows, build cloud-native applications, and integrate complex systems. My focus is on turning real-world
        problems into clean, reliable systems that are easy to operate, maintain, and evolve.
      </p>

      <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-10 text-gray-300">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What I Do</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-base">
            <li>Design <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">serverless architectures</span> and AWS-based microservices</li>
            <li>Build <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">automation tools</span> that reduce manual work and operational risk</li>
            <li>Create <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">scalable applications</span> across web, cloud, and desktop platforms</li>
            <li>Develop <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">dashboards and internal tooling</span> that improve visibility and workflows</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Areas of Expertise</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-base">
            <li><span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Telephony API integrations</span> (RingCentral, NICE inContact, 8x8)</li>
            <li><span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">HIPAA-compliant healthcare systems</span> and automation workflows</li>
            <li><span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Microservices and serverless</span> cloud architecture</li>
            <li><span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">REST APIs, webhooks,</span> and authentication systems</li>
            <li><span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Resilient distributed systems</span> with reliable error handling</li>
            <li><span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Operational automation</span> for data pipelines, alerts, and system workflows</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mt-4">
            I specialize in bridging data and automation between cloud platforms, enterprise tools, and complex operational environments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">How I Work</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-base">
            <li>Start with the business problem, then design the simplest reliable solution</li>
            <li>Build systems with proper automation, observability, and operational clarity</li>
            <li>Prefer maintainability, resilience, and clean engineering over quick hacks</li>
            <li>Use proven tools: Python, React, AWS, Docker, CI/CD pipelines</li>
            <li>Prioritize real-world reliability and low operational overhead</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Current Focus</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-base">
            <li>AI-assisted automation and intelligent workflows</li>
            <li>Serverless SaaS development and cloud-native solutions</li>
            <li>Professional freelance engineering and consulting</li>
            <li>Dashboard, telemetry, and operational tooling solutions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>